org.androidtransfuse.intentFactory
Interface IntentFactoryStrategy

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractIntentFactoryStrategy, ActivityIntentFactoryStrategy, ServiceIntentFactoryStrategy
public interface IntentFactoryStrategy

Strategy class defining a Contract for the given Android Context, specifying the relevant parameters to build an Android Intent.

Author:
John Ericksen

start

void start(android.content.Context context,
           android.content.Intent intent)
Starts the relevant Android Context component by Intent. The given Intent will be generated by the IntentFactory using parameters found in this instance.

Parameters:
context - current Context.
intent - built Intent.
